744
01:05:39.848 --> 01:05:40.679
Bambi.

745
01:05:40.723 --> 01:05:42.464
Aku berumur 26.

746
01:05:42.515 --> 01:05:44.366
Aku sudah bekerja mati-matian
di tambang kaleng-kaleng


747
01:05:44.390 --> 01:05:45.631
